tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE scanned_fingerprints (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    fingerprint_data BYTEA,
    scan_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE fingerprint_templates (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    template_data BYTEA,
    creation_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE fingerprint_matches (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    scanned_fingerprint_id UUID,
    matched_template_id UUID,
    match_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    password_hash BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE user_roles (
    role_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    role_name VARCHAR(50)
)
